# LLM Cost Estimator Project Requirements

## Overview

- LLM cost estimation tool to calculate costs based on prompt examples and request count
- Multilingual support (initially Japanese and English)
- Browser's default language setting will be used

## Technical Stack

- Next.js + TypeScript
- Static site deployment
- GitHub Pages hosting
- Token calculation libraries allowed
- CSV data management

## UI Components

### Input Section

- Prompt input example field
- Prompt output example field
- Request count input
- Language switching menu

### Output Section

- LLM provider (company name)
- Model name
- Model input pricing (per 1,000 tokens)
- Model output pricing (per 1,000 tokens)
- Estimated cost (USD) - sortable
- URL to pricing documentation

## Data Management

CSV format with the following fields:

- LLM provider (company name)
- Model name
- Input pricing (per 1,000 tokens)
- Output pricing (per 1,000 tokens)
- Estimated cost (USD)
- URL to pricing documentation
